title: Extinction: Zombie Survival v1.0.1_4577 Mod (Free Shopping)
description:
Can you survive the zombie onslaught?

Two mercenaries. One armory. Thousands of zombies coming to kill you. Turn your thumbs into lethal weapons and survive wave after wave of the walking dead!

Upload your score and top the Terminators' Leaderboard! Improve your weapons and discard the infected ones!

Features:

- Survive a zombie holocaust of hellish proportions!
- Easily control two mercenaries at the same time!
- Level up your weapons!
- Machine guns, flame-throwers, shotguns, pistols, grenades, mines, turrets: what more do you need?
- Will you be worthy of Chuck's admiration?
